import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; function Properties() { const [selectedBuyRent, setSelectedBuyRent] = useState("Buy"); const [selectedPropertyType, setSelectedPropertyType] = useState(""); const [subTypes, setSubTypes] = useState([]); const [allProperties, setAllProperties] = useState([]); // get alll Properties data useEffect(() => { // Fetch data when the component is mounted const fetchProperties = async () => { try { const response = await fetch( "https://localhost:7019/api/PropertiesApi/GetAllProperties" ); if (!response.ok) { throw new Error(`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`); } const data = await response.json(); setAllProperties(data); } catch (error) { console.log("Error fetching properties in fetch method:", error); } }; fetchProperties(); }, []); // for serch style const propertyTypes = [ { id: 1, name: "Residential" }, { id: 2, name: "Commercial" }, { id: 3, name: "Land" }, { id: 4, name: "Rental" }, ]; const propertySubTypes = { Residential: ["Apartment/Flat", "Independent House/Villa"], Commercial: ["Office Space", "Retail/Shop Space", "Warehouse/Godown"], Land: ["Residential Land", "Agricultural Land", "Commercial Land", "Industrial Plot"], Rental: ["Hostels", "PG", "Hotels/Resorts", "Apartment/Flat", "Independent House/Villa"], }; const handleBuyRentChange = (event) => { const value = event.target.value; setSelectedBuyRent(value); setSelectedPropertyType(""); if (value === "Rent") { setSubTypes(propertySubTypes["Rental"]); } else { setSubTypes([]); } }; const handlePropertyTypeChange = (event) => { const value = event.target.value; setSelectedPropertyType(value); setSubTypes(propertySubTypes[value] || []); }; // serch style end return ( <>
